{"id":"45a7ea1e-35f0-4dcb-975c-c62ae5fd594a","title":"1512/09/05: To Buonarroto di Lodovico Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"647ba578-95cb-4687-b8f8-9dc9067b1866","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, [September 5th, 1512].","standoffProperties":[{"id":"be449176-cff0-4260-864c-3c2d55181f2a","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":3,"value":"8532f2fa-b614-4eed-9eae-586327f6a15a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"320aa874-11df-413a-b3d1-a041c48525a1","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0d773053-cbfb-4040-87fc-f83f67b9a9f8","type":"codex/time-reference","start":12,"end":30,"value":"994edc96-adff-476d-94b2-3d1d6c8045cf","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"0864cf66-1e98-4958-a42a-0a0d574c1704","type":"style/superscript","start":23,"end":24,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"f5f1b076-e8f2-432b-a491-1c29ecf4eb61","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Buonarroto di Lodovico Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"910178c7-bbd3-42ea-b3f7-0369e57aa019","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"27762e55-3cfc-418d-9624-3dd74106257c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"eb5c2755-f869-4ca7-8733-1c39b95bc7a0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"5e70cd6f-cd57-475f-8743-b976f02f2bbb","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"86735ca5-729c-4c71-9c00-ca6faa280fff","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":1,"value":"0c663cc2-dd9f-40ce-b17b-734e41b369ef","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"e700cfef-d53d-4580-a9a6-951baccb578f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"5561922e-0ba5-4bc0-a61f-684d95ab7699","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"72abdd29-e883-4461-a908-b31e8f333302","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Buonarroto,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0I have not written to thee these last few days because there was no occasion for it:\u00A0but now, seeing the course matters are taking in\u00A0Florence, it seems advisable that I should speak out. As, judging by what people say here, the [Florentine]\u00A0Territory is in an evil plight, I think you ought all of you to retreat to some place where you will be in safety, abandoning all you possess: for life is more\u00A0precious than worldly gear. If you have not the\u00A0wherewithal to depart from Florence, go to the Spedalingo and make him give you money. If I were with you I should draw all my money from the\u00A0Spedalingo and go to Siena; there I should take a house and stay until matters had settled down again.\u00A0I believe the power of attorney I gave Lodovico has\u00A0not yet expired, so that it will enable him to withdraw my money. If there is any occasion for it, let him do this: and in all such moments of peril draw out and spend whatever may be necessary. The remainder you will keep for me. Do not under any\u00A0circumstances involve yourselves in the affairs of the\u00A0Territory, either by word or deed: do as ye would do if it were the plague\u00A0\u2014\u00A0be the first to flee. No more. Let me have news as quickly as thou canst for I am in a state of great anxiety.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"de17538b-9496-4ccd-b9e7-e31bc784497a","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":9,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c1f9373a-8640-4e8f-a32f-34be5b195387","type":"tei/textstructure/salute","start":0,"end":9,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"e64636e0-5147-481a-8aa7-85d234f2e5e6","type":"tei/textstructure/opener","start":0,"end":13,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b4fde36b-0797-41ce-a8c0-99be803c2a7c","type":"codex/entity-reference",